parameters.name: OMNIDIRECTIONAL-PROTON TELESCOPES
parameters.description: This column contains 4 items of proton flux from Omnidirectional-Protons (520-1423 keV) Telescopes 1-4 Spin Averages 1-4. Flux units are protons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: PRTL SECTOR DATA
parameters.description: This column contains 8 sectors of PRTL proton flux data. Flux units are protons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: ELTL1
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from Electrons Low (100-308 keV) Spin Averages Telescope 1. Flux units are electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: EHTL1
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from Electrons High (E > 180 keV) Spin Averages Telescope 1. Flux units are electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: ELTL2
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from Electrons Low (100-308 keV) Spin Averages Telescope 2. Flux units are electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: EHTL2
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from Electrons High (E > 180 keV) Spin Averages Telescope 2. Flux units are electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: ELTL3
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from Electrons Low (100-308 keV) Spin Averages Telescope 3. Flux units are electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: EHTL3
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from Electrons High (E > 180 keV) Spin Averages Telescope 3. Flux units are electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: ELTL4
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from Electrons Low (100-308 keV) Spin Averages Telescope 4. Flux units are electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: EHTL4
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from Electrons High (E > 180 keV) Spin Averages Telescope 4. Flux units are electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: ERL
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from the Event-Rate Low Omni- directional Channel.

parameters.name: ERM
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from the Event-Rate Medium Omnidirectional Channel.

parameters.name: ERH
parameters.description: This column contains electron flux from the Event-Rate High Omni-directional Channel.

parameters.name: PSTL SECTOR DATA
parameters.description: This column contains sector proton flux data for one channel of one of the Proton Spectral Telescopes (PSTL). Flux units are protons/(s cm^2 sr).
